	<ThingDef ParentName="UVVaultBase">
		<defName>UVVaultCemeteryS</defName>
		<label>cemetery underground vault</label>
		<description>Cemetery underground vault for storing sarcophagus. Size S.\n\nThings inside vault is safe from surrounding hazards. The surrounding soil preventing raiders from knowing what is inside the vault.</description>
